  "texts": [
    "Understanding these ideas can provide us with valuable contextual knowledge when evaluating the mechanisms of implications.",
    "For the purposes of this analysis, a concise-although reflectiveintroduction will do.",
    "According to Schopmans [13], the ETA in AI has ties to EA, which is a movement and a philosophy that-in their own words-\"aims to find the best ways to help others, and put them into practice\".",
    "8 Although seemingly innocuous, if not admirable, both the practices and the philosophy of the movement have received critique (see, e.g., the discussion of critiques in [24]).",
    "For example, the philosophical foundation of the movement stresses a \"duty to use a proportion of one's resources\" [25, p.xiii] on charitable pursuits."
